<!-- STEP 2: Listen -->
<div class="step" id="step-1">
  <div class="step-header" onclick="toggleStep(1)">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-title">Listen to the call</div>
    <div class="step-arrow">▶</div>
  </div>
  <div class="step-body">
    <p class="prose" id="listen-prose"></p>
    <div class="waveform-wrap">
      <div class="wave-label">Waveform — amplitude over time</div>
      <canvas class="waveform" id="waveform-canvas" width="800" height="80"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="waveform-wrap">
      <div class="wave-label">Spectrogram — frequency over time (brighter = louder)</div>
      <canvas class="spectrogram" id="spectrogram-canvas" width="800" height="120"></canvas>
    </div>
    <button class="play-btn" id="play-btn" onclick="playSound()">
      <span class="play-icon">▶</span> <span id="play-label">Play call</span>
    </button>
    <button class="next-btn" onclick="goStep(2)">Next: What did we just hear? →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STEP 3: Measure it -->
<div class="step" id="step-2">
  <div class="step-header" onclick="toggleStep(2)">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-title">Measure it</div>
    <div class="step-arrow">▶</div>
  </div>
  <div class="step-body">
    <p class="prose">
      Now CetaSignal measures the call — like a doctor taking vital signs. We extract <strong>10 acoustic features</strong>. Each one tells us something different about how the sound was made and what it might mean.
    </p>
    <button class="extract-btn" id="extract-btn" onclick="runExtraction()">
      ▶ Run Feature Extraction
    </button>
    <div class="features-grid" id="features-grid" style="display:none"></div>
    <button class="next-btn" id="next-2" onclick="goStep(3)" style="display:none">Next: Classify the behavior →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STEP 4: Classify -->
<div class="step" id="step-3">
  <div class="step-header" onclick="toggleStep(3)">
    <div class="step-num">4</div>
    <div class="step-title">Classify the behavior</div>
    <div class="step-arrow">▶</div>
  </div>
  <div class="step-body">
    <p class="prose">
      CetaSignal applies its <strong>constraint rules</strong> — not machine learning, not a black box. It checks the features against known patterns, step by step, and outputs one of five behavioral classes. Watch it decide.
    </p>
    <div id="rule-trace" style="margin:16px 0"></div>
    <div class="result-box" id="result-box">
      <div class="result-class" id="result-class"></div>
      <div class="result-name" id="result-name"></div>
      <div class="result-desc" id="result-desc"></div>
      <div class="confidence-bar">
        <div class="confidence-fill" id="conf-fill" style="width:0%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="confidence-label" id="conf-label"></div>
    </div>
    <button class="next-btn" id="next-3" onclick="goStep(4)" style="display:none">Next: See the specimen record →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STEP 5: Specimen output -->
<div class="step" id="step-4">
  <div class="step-header" onclick="toggleStep(4)">
