    </p>
    <div class="specimen-card" id="specimen-output"></div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p class="prose" style="text-align:center; color: var(--muted); font-size:12px">
      That's one specimen. CetaSignal has processed <strong style="color:var(--bright)">5,000</strong> of them —<br>
      across <strong style="color:var(--bright)">19 species</strong>, <strong style="color:var(--bright)">11 ocean basins</strong>, <strong style="color:var(--bright)">9 public datasets</strong>.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px">
